id: pm-646c
title: "NDJSON output mode: --format ndjson on list/search/context emits one JSON object per line for grep/jq/xargs pipelines"
description: "Line-oriented output child of the composability story: current json/toon/csv/table formats are document-shaped, so jq streaming and grep-per-item need awkward preprocessing. NDJSON is the standard pipeline interchange. Related: pm-cfed (lean JSON field shape) composes with this; pagination cursor work (pm-dfg0) shares ordering guarantees."
